artin Delgado]] <!-- PNP -->\n| [[Iloilo City]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Francisco C. Fernandez Jr.]] <!-- PNP -->\n| data-sort-value=\"Sibulan, Negros Oriental\" | Agan-an, [[Sibulan, Negros Oriental]]\n\n<!-- Mindanao: -->\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp General Basilio Navarro]]\n| [[Zamboanga City]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Panacan - Naval Station Felix Apolinario]]\n| data-sort-value=\"Davao City, Panacan\" | Panacan, [[Davao City]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Cagayan De Oro#Law and order|Camp Edilberto Evangelista]]\n| data-sort-value=\"Cagayan de Oro\" | Patag, [[Cagayan de Oro]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Major Cesar L. Sang-an]]\n| data-sort-value=\"Labangan, Zamboanga del Sur\" | Pulacan, [[Labangan, Zamboanga del Sur]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Colonel Oscar F. Natividad]]\n| [[Manolo Fortich, Bukidnon]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Osito D. Bahian]]\n| [[Malaybalay, Bukidnon]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Ranao]]\n| [[Marawi City]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Allere]]\n| [[Salvador, Lanao del Norte]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Duma Sinsuat]]\n| [[Barira, Maguindanao]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Brig. Gen. Gonzalo H. Siongco]]\n| [[Datu Odin Sinsuat, Maguindanao]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Robert Eduard M. Lucero]]\n| data-sort-value=\"Carmen, Cotabato\" | Nasapian, [[Carmen, Cotabato|Carmen]], [[Cotabato]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Paulino Santos]]\n| data-sort-value=\"Alamada, Cotabato\" | Dado, [[Alamada, Cotabato]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Brig. Gen. Hermenegildo Agaab]]\n| data-sort-value=\"Malungon, Sarangani\" | Malandag, [[Malungon, Sarangani]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Overton (Philippines)|Camp Overton]]\n| data-sort-value=\"Iligan\" | Suarez, [[Iligan]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Fermin G. Lira, Jr.]]\n| data-sort-value=\"General Santos\" | Bulaong Road, [[General Santos]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Torrey Barracks]]\n| [[Malabang, Lanao del Sur]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Camp Amai Pakpak]]\n| [[Marawi, Lanao del Sur]]\n